            Accessing the center is easy. We are just a couple of blocks away from both major freeways. Our parents enter the center through a secure parking garage and keypad entry. Free parking is provided. Visitors with appointments are provided with a QR code to grant them access to the center. Unauthorized visitors without appointments must speak to security to gain access. 
